<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْوَاقِعَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٤٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {إِذَا وَقَعَتِ الْوَاقِعَةُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> لَيْسَ لِوَقْعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> خَافِضَةٌ رَافِعَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> إِذَا رُجَّتِ الْأَرْضُ رَجًّا <span class="c2">(٤)</span> وَبُسَّتِ الْجِبَالُ بَسًّا <span class="c2">(٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[الواقعة: ١ - ٥]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{خَافِضَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لِقَوْمٍ إِلَى النَّارِ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{رَافِعَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«إِلَى الجَنَّةِ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{رُجَّتْ}</span>: <span class="c2">«زُلْزِلَتْ»</span>،<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{بُسَّتْ}</span>: " فُتَّتْ , لُتَّتْ , كَمَا يُلَتُّ السَّوِيقُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>